INSTRUCTION TO PLAYERS:


Rule:
Winner is the first player to get an continous row of four LEDs on horizontally,vertically,or diagonally.

Draw could be resulted when all the matrix is too full to a light further LED.



Placing led:
Press the navigational switch up(North): row ++.
press the navigational switch down(South) : row--;
Press the navigational switch right(East): column ++.
press the navigational switch left(West) : column--;
press the navigational switch push: flash the corresponding on another player's board.

Display led matrix:
Setted LED will not flash.
Received LED will flash.

Others:
If players want to set an unavailable LED(The LED is setted or received), the LED will not flash on another player's board when pressing the navigational switch push.




